---
title: Smart Bacon-Wrapped Green Beans with Salad and Avocado Dressing
description: Everything's better with bacon! Tonight, you'll wrap tender green beans in strips of smoky bacon so they can roast together and become charming bundles of fun! A bright salad comes alongside with hard boiled eggs for additional protein.

Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's kilocalorie and carbohydrate amounts.
